

Kafka : distributed sreaming platform
	> apache product
	> streaming platform = 
		> pub/sub to streams
		> store streams in fault tolerant way
		> process streams as they occur
	> uses :
		> pipeline for streaming data
		> transforming streaming data

	> details
		> stream comprised of records
		> streams stored in categories called topics
		> each record has key, value, timestamp

	> APIs
		> producer : an application that publishes data to one of Kafka's topics
		> consumer : an application that stubcsribes to one or more topics
		> streams : an application can act as a processor. Input comes from a topic, and output goes to another topic
		> connector : connect topics to existing data systems

